OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777057867
OL,3,CFormer councillor involved in
OL,4,Cchildren's services jailed for child
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FA former Dudley councillor, who sat on
OL,8,Fthe Children's Services Committee, has
OL,9,Fbeen sentenced after admitting four
OL,10,Fsexual offences involving children.
OL,12,FAdrian Hughes was caught by a police
OL,13,Foperation where officers impersonated
OL,14,Ftwo girls, one aged 12 and the other
OL,15,Faged 13.
OL,17,FHughes admitted to attempting to
OL,18,Finitiate non-penetrative sexual
OL,19,Factivity with a girl under 13 and a
OL,20,Fgirl aged 13 to 15.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777057867
OL,3,CFormer councillor involved in
OL,4,Cchildren's services jailed for child
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FHe also admitted charges of attempting
OL,8,Fto engage in sexual communication with
OL,9,Fa child aged under 13 and with a child
OL,10,Faged 13 to 15.
OL,12,FThe offences took place during May and
OL,13,FJune 2025 when law enforcement
OL,14,Fofficers created the characters of
OL,15,FLucy, aged 13 and Molly, aged 12 on
OL,16,Fthe online platforms IB and Kick.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777057867
OL,3,CFormer councillor involved in
OL,4,Cchildren's services jailed for child
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FMiss Recorder A Siddiqi said: "You
OL,8,Fthought you were messaging 12 and 13-
OL,9,Fyear-olds, you could have done a great
OL,10,Fdeal of harm, unacceptable does not
OL,11,Fcapture how appalling your behaviour
OL,12,Fwas; immediate custody was inevitable."
OL,14,FHughes was suspended from the Labour
OL,15,FParty in October 2023 following an
OL,16,Fundisclosed complaint about his
OL,17,Fbehaviour which was the subject of a
OL,18,Fparty investigation.
OL,26,@oD@_OUtD@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777057867
OL,3,CFormer councillor involved in
OL,4,Cchildren's services jailed for child
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FHe sat on the Children's Services
OL,8,FSelect Committee and the Overview and
OL,9,FScrutiny Committee from May to
OL,10,FSeptember 2023.
OL,12,FHe was a member of the Children and
OL,13,FYoung Person's Scrutiny Committee from
OL,14,FMay 2022 to May 2023 and also the
OL,15,FChildren's Corporate Parenting Board
OL,16,Ffrom May 2022 to May 2023.
OL,18,FProsecutor James Cooper told the court
OL,19,FHughes, who was a Labour councillor in
OL,20,FDudley from 2022 until 2024, first
OL,21,Fmade contact with 'Lucy'.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777057867
OL,3,CFormer councillor involved in
OL,4,Cchildren's services jailed for child
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FDespite 'Lucy' telling Hughes she was
OL,8,F13 he asked for pictures of her, said
OL,9,Fshe had an 'amazing body' and sent her
OL,10,Fsexually explicit messages.
OL,12,FHughes then started a chat with
OL,13,F'Molly' and again asked for pictures,
OL,14,Fofficers sent a fake image of a fully-
OL,15,Fclothed girl and Hughes responded by
OL,16,Fasking her to remove her hoodie.
OL,18,FHe said she was too young for him and
OL,19,Fbroke off contact but then messaged
OL,20,Fher again on six more occasions.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777057867
OL,3,CFormer councillor involved in
OL,4,Cchildren's services jailed for child
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FAfter talking about 'grown ups' having
OL,8,Fsex Hughes sent 'Molly' images of him
OL,9,Fin his underwear and of his genitals.
OL,11,FEventually police identified Hughes
OL,12,Fand he was arrested on June 23, 2025.
OL,14,FGeorgia Faulke, for the defence, told
OL,15,Fthe court Hughes was of previous good
OL,16,Fcharacter and the offending took place
OL,17,Fover a short time when her client, who
OL,18,Fgrew up with parents who misused
OL,19,Falcohol, was suffering mental health
OL,20,Fproblems.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777057867
OL,3,CFormer councillor involved in
OL,4,Cchildren's services jailed for child
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FMiss Faulke said: "It was a period of
OL,8,Fisolation, he wanted support from
OL,9,Fsomeone, someone to talk to.
OL,11,F"It stems from mental health
OL,12,Fdifficulties he was going through at
OL,13,Fthe time."
OL,15,FThe court also heard, during the
OL,16,Foffending, Hughes was self-medicating
OL,17,Fwith cocaine, cannabis and alcohol but
OL,18,Fwas now free from drugs and had
OL,19,Fdramatically reduced his drinking.
OL,26,@oD@SOUsD@AOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777057867
OL,3,CFormer councillor involved in
OL,4,Cchildren's services jailed for child
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FMiss Faulke added Hughes, who showed
OL,8,Fno emotion in the dock, had not re-
OL,9,Foffended since his arrest and was
OL,10,Fexperiencing remorse for his actions.
OL,12,FRecorder Siddiqi sentenced Hughes to
OL,13,F32 months in jail for attempting to
OL,14,Fincite a child into sexual activity
OL,15,Fand terms of 12, 15 and 12 months to
OL,16,Frun concurrently for the other three
OL,17,Foffences.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777057867
OL,3,CFormer councillor involved in
OL,4,Cchildren's services jailed for child
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FHe was given credit for admitting his
OL,8,Fcrimes at the first opportunity but
OL,9,Fwas told he tried to conceal evidence
OL,10,Fby deleting some of the chats from his
OL,11,Fphone, which was an aggravating
OL,12,Ffeature.
OL,14,FHe was also made the subject of an
OL,15,Findefinite Sexual Harm Prevention
OL,16,FOrder and ordered to inform police of
OL,17,Fhis address and any change of name,
OL,18,Falso for an indefinite period.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
